-- Pirelli Chairman Tronchetti Sees Tyre Sales Up 15%, `Maybe Even Better'
-- B y   M a r c o   B e r t a c c h e
-- 2010-09-23T11:23:30Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-09-23/pirelli-chairman-tronchetti-sees-tyre-sales-up-15-maybe-even-better-.html
Pirelli & C. SpA Chairman Marco
Tronchetti Provera forecast 2010 tyre sales “will rise 15
percent, maybe even better,” speaking at a presentation in
Izmit, Turkey. Pirelli had a forecast of 2010 tyre sales growth
of as much as 15 percent.  The company plans to present its new business plan on Nov.
4, Tronchetti said. His comments were confirmed by a company
official.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Marco Bertacche at 
 mbertacche@bloomberg.net  